## Naming conventions

| Artifact | Convention |
|----------|-----------|
| DB entity type | `DB_PasskeyCredential` |
| DB def | `DBDef_PasskeyCredential` |
| Database def type | `DatabaseDef_PasskeyCredential` |
| Backend auth module | `ModuleBE_PasskeyAuth` |
| Backend credential DB module | `ModuleBE_PasskeyCredentialDB` |
| Frontend auth module | `ModuleFE_PasskeyAuth` |
| Frontend credential DB module | `ModuleFE_PasskeyCredentialDB` |
| Backend module pack | `ModulePackBE_Passkey` |
| Frontend module pack | `ModulePackFE_Passkey` |
| API type | `API_Passkey` |
| API def constant | `ApiDef_Passkey` |
| Login component | `Component_PasskeyLogin` |
| Register component | `Component_PasskeyRegister` |
| Credential list component | `Component_PasskeyCredentials` |

